media:group.media:title: The EA Inclusion Survey
media:group.media:description:
Electronic Arts, in their attempt to seem trendy and gather into their stock more paying customers, tries desperately to explain that “inclusion” in their video games is definitely a totally super important thing gamers want right after Battlefield 5 did so well.
